                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "Était-ce aux bords du Sund ? aux côtes de Bretagne ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Aviez-vous l'océan au pied de la montagne ?",
